{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/dizziness-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/dizziness-and-driving","title":"Dizziness (giddiness) and driving","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2404","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"You must tell DVLA if you suffer from dizziness - cars, motorbikes, buses, coaches, lorries, medical information, forms","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you suffer from dizziness.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<h3>Vertebrobasilar giddiness</h3>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form B1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_066652.pdf\" title=\"Download 'B1 - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 3115KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘B1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 315KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>Other diziness/giddiness</h3>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form DIZ1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065610.pdf\" title=\"Download 'DIZ1 - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 182KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘DIZ1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 182KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<h3>Vertebrobasilar giddiness</h3>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in forms B1 and FEB1V and send them to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the forms.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_066652.pdf\" title=\"Download 'B1 - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 3115KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘B1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 315KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_185934.pdf\" title=\"Download 'FEB1V - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 355KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘FEP1V - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 355KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>Other diziness/giddiness</h3>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form DIZ1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_4018276.pdf\" title=\"Download 'DIZ1V - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 261KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘DIZ1V - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 261KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:15:40+00:00","tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"786","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:20:40+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"13","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:25:48+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Giving up your driving licence","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2390","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:17:07+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2399","business_proposition":true},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:15:05+00:00"}]}